{"video_id": "JiUwk_OyRrM", "title": "Srimad Bhagavatam I Sri Satya Guara Chandra Dasa I SB 3.6.35 I 02.06.2022", "speaker": "HG Satya Gaura Chandra Dasa", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JiUwk_OyRrM", "duration": 1591, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 3.7, "text": " Om Namo Bhadravate Vasudevaya"}, {"start": 3.7, "end": 13.42, "text": " Reading from Srimad Bhatavatam, 10-3, Chapter 6, Verse 35"}, {"start": 13.42, "end": 16.26, "text": " Etat Satar Bhadravato"}, {"start": 16.26, "end": 21.42, "text": " Daiva Tarmatma Rupinaha"}, {"start": 21.42, "end": 26.8, "text": " Rahasraddhatyad Upatrartum"}, {"start": 26.8, "end": 31.92, "text": " Yodramaya Balodayam"}, {"start": 31.92, "end": 40.44, "text": " Translation and perfect by His Divine Rest, Srila Prabhupada"}, {"start": 40.44, "end": 43.040000000000006, "text": " Translation"}, {"start": 43.040000000000006, "end": 49.519999999999996, "text": " O Vidura, who can estimate or measure the transcendental time,"}, {"start": 49.519999999999996, "end": 53.32, "text": " work and potency of the gigantic form"}, {"start": 53.32, "end": 56.120000000000005, "text": " manifested by the internal potency"}, {"start": 56.120000000000005, "end": 56.78, "text": " of the transcendental form"}, {"start": 56.78, "end": 56.8, "text": " of the transcendental form."}, {"start": 56.800000000000004, "end": 58.64000000000001, "text": " of the supreme personality of Godhead."}, {"start": 59.220000000000006, "end": 60.68000000000001, "text": " Perfect by Srila Prabhupada."}, {"start": 62.660000000000004, "end": 64.14, "text": " The fraudist philosophers"}, {"start": 64.14, "end": 67.06, "text": " may go on with their mental speculation"}, {"start": 67.06, "end": 69.86, "text": " on the subject matter of the Virat,"}, {"start": 70.4, "end": 72.08000000000001, "text": " the gigantic form exhibited"}, {"start": 72.08000000000001, "end": 75.94, "text": " by the Yodramaya internal potency"}, {"start": 75.94, "end": 77.92, "text": " of the supreme personality of Godhead."}, {"start": 78.64, "end": 81.32000000000001, "text": " But factually, no one can measure"}, {"start": 81.32000000000001, "end": 83.52000000000001, "text": " such a vast exhibition."}, {"start": 83.52000000000001, "end": 86.52000000000001, "text": " In Bhagavad Gita 11.16,"}, {"start": 86.8, "end": 93.17999999999999, "text": " Arjuna the recognized devotee of the Lord, says,"}, {"start": 93.17999999999999, "end": 114.53999999999999, "text": " planetary"}, {"start": 114.54, "end": 128.12, "text": " bodies, mouths, and eyes in all directions, and they are all unlimited. I cannot find the end of this manifestation, nor do I see the middle, nor the beginning."}, {"start": 128.12, "end": 150.64000000000001, "text": " But Vajritha was specifically spoken to Arjuna, and the Vishwarupa was exhibited before him at his request. He was awarded the specific eyes to see this Vishwarupa, yet although he was able to see the Lord's innumerable hands and mouths, he was unable to see him completely."}, {"start": 150.88, "end": 158.1, "text": " Since Arjuna was unable to estimate the length and breadth of the potency of the Lord, who else would be able to do so?"}, {"start": 158.12, "end": 186.36, "text": " One may only indulge in miscalculation like the fraught philosopher. The fraught philosopher wanted to estimate the length and breadth of the Pacific Ocean by his experience of the well, well three cubic feet large, and thus he began to puff himself up to become as big as the Pacific Ocean, but at last he burst and died by this process."}, {"start": 186.36, "end": 188.1, "text": " This is his story."}, {"start": 188.12, "end": 200.18, "text": " This story is applicable to the mental philosopher who, under the illusion of the Lord's external energy, indulges in estimating the length and breadth of the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 200.18, "end": 215.8, "text": " The best path is to become a cruel-headed, submissive devotee of the Lord. Try to hear about the Lord from the bona fide spiritual master, and thus serve the Lord in transcendental loving service, as suggested in the previous verse."}, {"start": 216.36, "end": 217.98000000000002, "text": " Thus ends the Vattivedanta Purport."}, {"start": 218.12, "end": 231.52, "text": " So, in our day-to-day life, we will be meeting a lot of people while traveling or while visiting some other place."}, {"start": 233.66, "end": 237.82, "text": " Sometimes we will be introduced to some unknown people."}, {"start": 239.12, "end": 248.06, "text": " So, of course, in the modern world, particularly in a corporate world, as soon as we meet one more,"}, {"start": 248.12, "end": 255.58, "text": " the more likely we are to meet one person, the more likely we are to meet one person."}, {"start": 255.58, "end": 261.98, "text": " If we meet one and the same person, immediately they exchange cards."}, {"start": 261.98, "end": 266.78000000000003, "text": " They exchange visiting cards, and both of them will come to know who are they, will"}, {"start": 266.78000000000003, "end": 271.56, "text": " come to know what is the other person, the other person also will come to know."}, {"start": 271.56, "end": 276.12, "text": " Another is that, we have left for a long time, and we have to be a little more aware of what our true soul is and how the soul of this soul works."}, {"start": 276.12, "end": 277.64, "text": " We have to be in the state of being."}, {"start": 277.64, "end": 282.97999999999996, "text": " you are not sure how to deal with him or how to relate with him, right?"}, {"start": 282.97999999999996, "end": 290.94, "text": " So the mind starts thinking, who is he, what kind of a person is he?"}, {"start": 291.52, "end": 295.21999999999997, "text": " The mind starts calculating about the other person."}, {"start": 296.53999999999996, "end": 300.97999999999996, "text": " And the process of calculation is that we will be estimating,"}, {"start": 301.09999999999997, "end": 303.26, "text": " okay, he may be like this, he may be like that."}, {"start": 303.26, "end": 310.78, "text": " But if a card is given, you know, this process can stop"}, {"start": 310.78, "end": 312.86, "text": " and then we can make up our mind, okay,"}, {"start": 313.78, "end": 319.03999999999996, "text": " looks like he is quite powerful than me or he is quite senior to me"}, {"start": 319.03999999999996, "end": 321.71999999999997, "text": " and then immediately, accordingly, we will behave."}, {"start": 322.4, "end": 323.71999999999997, "text": " See, our next steps are pending."}, {"start": 324.44, "end": 329.0, "text": " Next steps are dependent on our estimation of the other person."}, {"start": 329.36, "end": 331.26, "text": " It's a natural process."}, {"start": 331.26, "end": 336.65999999999997, "text": " Next steps are the process in which our brain works,"}, {"start": 338.08, "end": 339.18, "text": " the material brain works."}, {"start": 341.82, "end": 353.59999999999997, "text": " So, if a person is told about God as a person,"}, {"start": 354.32, "end": 356.14, "text": " God as a personality,"}, {"start": 356.14, "end": 359.88, "text": " then again the mind starts working."}, {"start": 361.26, "end": 364.36, "text": " How, what kind of a personality is?"}, {"start": 366.82, "end": 368.78, "text": " Now, let us say you are a software engineer"}, {"start": 368.78, "end": 374.52, "text": " and then you come across one more person, he is also a software engineer."}, {"start": 374.7, "end": 379.98, "text": " Then you will try to see, you will try to position him, okay."}, {"start": 381.09999999999997, "end": 389.74, "text": " You know, is he equal to me or is he bigger than me or he is less than me?"}, {"start": 390.0, "end": 391.18, "text": " Always this calculation."}, {"start": 391.18, "end": 391.2, "text": " Always this calculation."}, {"start": 391.2, "end": 391.24, "text": " Always this calculation."}, {"start": 391.24, "end": 391.26, "text": " Always this calculation."}, {"start": 391.26, "end": 392.06, "text": " Always this calculation is there."}, {"start": 393.15999999999997, "end": 395.86, "text": " Even in Vaishnava community, we have this division."}, {"start": 397.64, "end": 401.84, "text": " Seniors are there, juniors are there and equals are there."}, {"start": 402.26, "end": 403.74, "text": " This calculation is there always."}, {"start": 406.86, "end": 411.86, "text": " And according to our estimation, if he is a bigger software engineer,"}, {"start": 412.78, "end": 415.08, "text": " that means having a bigger position or whatever,"}, {"start": 416.59999999999997, "end": 418.52, "text": " then accordingly we will talk."}, {"start": 419.28, "end": 420.46, "text": " We will immediately seek"}, {"start": 420.46, "end": 421.24, "text": " the information that we have."}, {"start": 421.8, "end": 425.90000000000003, "text": " Seek to understand what is he doing, how big the project is."}, {"start": 428.6, "end": 433.1, "text": " Is it double the project that I am doing or triple the project that I am doing?"}, {"start": 434.34000000000003, "end": 435.84000000000003, "text": " Particularly in terms of the money."}, {"start": 437.5, "end": 441.1, "text": " You know, to get an idea, you know, how to relate with this person."}, {"start": 443.38, "end": 448.92, "text": " So, if such people are told about God, about Krishna as a person,"}, {"start": 448.92, "end": 457.16, "text": " then immediately, mind will start thinking, okay, Krishna is a personality."}, {"start": 457.16, "end": 459.90000000000003, "text": " So, how big is the personality?"}, {"start": 462.8, "end": 464.16, "text": " Some people say we are equal."}, {"start": 466.16, "end": 468.84000000000003, "text": " These mayavadis, they'll say, we're all equal."}, {"start": 469.56, "end": 470.68, "text": " I am God, you are God."}, {"start": 471.90000000000003, "end": 474.58000000000004, "text": " So they, they try to make it equal."}, {"start": 477.08000000000004, "end": 478.46000000000004, "text": " They don't want to accept that."}, {"start": 478.46000000000004, "end": 481.78000000000003, "text": " The Lord can be all-powerful."}, {"start": 483.34000000000003, "end": 484.08000000000004, "text": " They have no idea."}, {"start": 485.58000000000004, "end": 490.12000000000006, "text": " So Prabhupada gives, he always uses this word called frog philosopher."}, {"start": 491.76000000000005, "end": 496.62000000000006, "text": " There are many philosophers in this world, they try to understand who is the supreme person."}, {"start": 498.62000000000006, "end": 506.78000000000003, "text": " Even in some religion, they, they know that the supreme person means he must be the original person,"}, {"start": 507.16, "end": 508.36, "text": " the oldest of the persons."}, {"start": 508.46000000000004, "end": 516.7, "text": " And then they depict him as an old man, a very old man with a white beard and all that."}, {"start": 521.74, "end": 527.14, "text": " Even Brahma Samhita says he is Purana Purusha."}, {"start": 528.98, "end": 532.24, "text": " Why he is called Purana Purusha, Adhyam?"}, {"start": 532.36, "end": 533.38, "text": " Because he is the origin."}, {"start": 535.2, "end": 537.34, "text": " Krishna is the origin of everything."}, {"start": 537.34, "end": 537.44, "text": " He is the origin of everything."}, {"start": 538.46, "end": 548.7, "text": " Satyamparam Dheemahi, this is a Gayathri word, Satyamparam is the supreme truth, he is the original person."}, {"start": 550.24, "end": 554.64, "text": " So then he is Purana Purusham, then obviously he is the oldest of the personalities."}, {"start": 556.38, "end": 568.14, "text": " But immediately it says, Purana Purusham Navayavanamcha, because as soon as the verse says that he is Purana Purusha, oldest,"}, {"start": 568.46, "end": 575.64, "text": " then immediately, our Minds will start painting, an old man with a long beard, the beard must be one mile or something"}, {"start": 581.26, "end": 584.34, "text": " you know, he must be having a lot of...you know all those things."}, {"start": 584.34, "end": 588.5, "text": " This is...you know the Mind goes on like that decoration."}, {"start": 588.5, "end": 590.64, "text": " So immediately it says, Navayavanamcha."}, {"start": 590.64, "end": 593.24, "text": " But, he is always youthful."}, {"start": 593.24, "end": 597.32, "text": " He is the oldest of persons, but he is always youthful."}, {"start": 597.32, "end": 597.84, "text": " that is process."}, {"start": 597.86, "end": 598.08, "text": " It is just miserable."}, {"start": 598.08, "end": 598.1800000000001, "text": " It is same as what we talk about, the process of becoming drunk, the process of becoming strong."}, {"start": 598.1800000000001, "end": 598.32, "text": " it is the process."}, {"start": 598.32, "end": 606.32, "text": " Prabhupada says at the time of the battlefield, the Kurukshetra battle,"}, {"start": 606.32, "end": 612.32, "text": " Krishna must be about 125 years old, according to material estimation,"}, {"start": 612.32, "end": 619.32, "text": " but He looks like a 16-20 years personality."}, {"start": 619.32, "end": 626.32, "text": " He appears to be growing from the childhood to adulthood to youth,"}, {"start": 626.32, "end": 632.32, "text": " but then beyond youth He doesn't grow."}, {"start": 632.32, "end": 636.32, "text": " You saw that? So that means He is a different personality."}, {"start": 636.32, "end": 639.32, "text": " So you should see the difference."}, {"start": 639.32, "end": 644.32, "text": " Simply because He has some two hands and two legs,"}, {"start": 644.32, "end": 647.32, "text": " and we also have two hands and two legs,"}, {"start": 647.32, "end": 652.32, "text": " it doesn't mean, you know, both are same."}, {"start": 652.32, "end": 654.32, "text": " You should see, okay,"}, {"start": 654.32, "end": 655.32, "text": " beyond youth,"}, {"start": 655.32, "end": 658.32, "text": " He is not growing."}, {"start": 658.32, "end": 663.32, "text": " No, you don't see anywhere Krishna depicted as an old man."}, {"start": 663.32, "end": 668.32, "text": " Right? That means He is a different personality."}, {"start": 668.32, "end": 675.32, "text": " In this world, to come across such a different personality is a great fortune."}, {"start": 675.32, "end": 679.32, "text": " You don't find, here everybody is a conditioned soul,"}, {"start": 679.32, "end": 683.32, "text": " with so many weaknesses and frailties."}, {"start": 683.32, "end": 691.32, "text": " To find God in front of you, that is not ordinary."}, {"start": 691.32, "end": 699.32, "text": " But the frog philosophers, they will not stop the calculation."}, {"start": 699.32, "end": 702.32, "text": " Prabhupada explains this tendency,"}, {"start": 702.32, "end": 712.32, "text": " and Parvati is explaining that there is one frog in a well of three cubic feet."}, {"start": 713.32, "end": 717.32, "text": " Just, you know, all over three, three feet well."}, {"start": 717.32, "end": 725.32, "text": " And one day, one more frog fell into that well."}, {"start": 725.32, "end": 729.32, "text": " And so obviously this frog,"}, {"start": 729.32, "end": 733.32, "text": " you know, the frog in the well started asking,"}, {"start": 733.32, "end": 735.32, "text": " okay, who are you?"}, {"start": 735.32, "end": 737.32, "text": " Where do you come from?"}, {"start": 737.32, "end": 740.32, "text": " It's like we have an estimation."}, {"start": 740.32, "end": 742.32, "text": " It is also trying to estimate who this frog is."}, {"start": 743.32, "end": 750.32, "text": " So he said, no, I am coming from the Pacific Ocean."}, {"start": 750.32, "end": 753.32, "text": " You know, I live nearby."}, {"start": 753.32, "end": 757.32, "text": " Actually frogs don't live in oceans."}, {"start": 757.32, "end": 760.32, "text": " So it saw the Pacific Ocean."}, {"start": 760.32, "end": 763.32, "text": " And it falls into this."}, {"start": 763.32, "end": 770.32, "text": " And so it says, you know, I come from a place, the Pacific Ocean."}, {"start": 770.32, "end": 773.32, "text": " Then the frog in the well says,"}, {"start": 773.32, "end": 775.32, "text": " what is this Pacific Ocean?"}, {"start": 775.32, "end": 779.32, "text": " No, no, very big."}, {"start": 779.32, "end": 781.32, "text": " Then it says, how big is that?"}, {"start": 781.32, "end": 782.32, "text": " Very big."}, {"start": 782.32, "end": 785.32, "text": " It's a very vast ocean."}, {"start": 785.32, "end": 789.32, "text": " And immediately the well frog is saying,"}, {"start": 789.32, "end": 791.32, "text": " how big is that?"}, {"start": 791.32, "end": 793.32, "text": " Is it three feet?"}, {"start": 793.32, "end": 794.32, "text": " No."}, {"start": 794.32, "end": 795.32, "text": " Ten feet?"}, {"start": 795.32, "end": 796.32, "text": " No."}, {"start": 796.32, "end": 797.32, "text": " Hundred feet?"}, {"start": 797.32, "end": 798.32, "text": " No."}, {"start": 798.32, "end": 801.32, "text": " Prabhupada says, ultimately it burst"}, {"start": 801.32, "end": 802.32, "text": " and died."}, {"start": 802.32, "end": 805.32, "text": " And died by his own process."}, {"start": 805.32, "end": 809.32, "text": " It is puffing, trying to show how big is that."}, {"start": 809.32, "end": 815.32, "text": " It is calculating in terms of feet."}, {"start": 815.32, "end": 819.32, "text": " Calculating in terms of the feet."}, {"start": 819.32, "end": 821.32, "text": " How long you can go on?"}, {"start": 821.32, "end": 824.32, "text": " Even million feet is less."}, {"start": 824.32, "end": 830.32, "text": " So similarly, when you see a personality,"}, {"start": 830.32, "end": 833.32, "text": " the personality of Krishna,"}, {"start": 833.32, "end": 838.32, "text": " then the philosophers, they try to calculate like this."}, {"start": 838.32, "end": 841.32, "text": " Maybe he is little better than me."}, {"start": 841.32, "end": 847.32, "text": " Generally, we estimate in terms of opulences."}, {"start": 847.32, "end": 850.32, "text": " Whether he is more stronger than me,"}, {"start": 850.32, "end": 853.32, "text": " or whether he is more powerful than me,"}, {"start": 853.32, "end": 855.32, "text": " or is more wealthier than me,"}, {"start": 855.32, "end": 857.32, "text": " or equal to me."}, {"start": 857.32, "end": 859.32, "text": " In terms of the six opulences,"}, {"start": 859.32, "end": 862.32, "text": " we will be calculating and trying to estimate"}, {"start": 862.32, "end": 865.32, "text": " where he stands."}, {"start": 865.32, "end": 867.32, "text": " In terms of money, it is easy."}, {"start": 867.32, "end": 871.32, "text": " You can put a number and see where you come."}, {"start": 871.32, "end": 873.32, "text": " That's what the Forbes magazine do"}, {"start": 873.32, "end": 876.32, "text": " every month or every quarter."}, {"start": 876.32, "end": 879.32, "text": " They put all the wealth of the richest people"}, {"start": 879.32, "end": 880.32, "text": " and then they will say,"}, {"start": 880.32, "end": 881.32, "text": " okay, you are number one, you are number two."}, {"start": 881.32, "end": 883.32, "text": " It's easy."}, {"start": 883.32, "end": 886.32, "text": " There is a system like that."}, {"start": 886.32, "end": 888.32, "text": " So, they compare."}, {"start": 888.32, "end": 891.32, "text": " Now, compare in terms of the opulences"}, {"start": 891.32, "end": 895.32, "text": " to estimate, okay, where he stands."}, {"start": 895.32, "end": 900.32, "text": " Now, what about the opulences of Krishna?"}, {"start": 900.32, "end": 903.32, "text": " So, can you estimate?"}, {"start": 903.32, "end": 908.32, "text": " The richest man has some hundred billion dollars,"}, {"start": 908.32, "end": 911.32, "text": " for example."}, {"start": 911.32, "end": 913.32, "text": " That will be for a month."}, {"start": 913.32, "end": 915.32, "text": " Next month we have to see."}, {"start": 915.32, "end": 917.32, "text": " And then hundred billion dollars."}, {"start": 917.32, "end": 918.32, "text": " And then let us say,"}, {"start": 918.32, "end": 920.32, "text": " he starts estimating"}, {"start": 920.32, "end": 923.32, "text": " how much Krishna has."}, {"start": 923.32, "end": 928.32, "text": " So, that process is called"}, {"start": 928.32, "end": 930.32, "text": " this Kupa Manduka Nyaya,"}, {"start": 930.32, "end": 932.32, "text": " the frog philosophy."}, {"start": 932.32, "end": 935.32, "text": " Nobody can estimate the opulences of Krishna."}, {"start": 935.32, "end": 938.32, "text": " You cannot even estimate"}, {"start": 938.32, "end": 942.32, "text": " how big is this universe."}, {"start": 942.32, "end": 945.32, "text": " How many planets are there in this universe?"}, {"start": 945.32, "end": 946.32, "text": " One cannot even estimate."}, {"start": 946.32, "end": 953.32, "text": " The most qualified person, Arjuna,"}, {"start": 953.32, "end": 955.32, "text": " he himself is saying,"}, {"start": 955.32, "end": 961.32, "text": " na antam na madhyam na punastha tava adhyam"}, {"start": 961.32, "end": 965.32, "text": " I am unable to perceive your Adhi,"}, {"start": 965.32, "end": 968.32, "text": " Madhyam and Anta."}, {"start": 968.32, "end": 969.32, "text": " Now, this is,"}, {"start": 969.32, "end": 973.32, "text": " Arjuna is referring to the gigantic Vishwaroopa,"}, {"start": 973.32, "end": 975.32, "text": " Virata form."}, {"start": 975.32, "end": 980.32, "text": " And when Arjuna asks Krishna,"}, {"start": 980.32, "end": 983.32, "text": " Krishna, I want to see your universal form,"}, {"start": 983.32, "end": 987.32, "text": " the form which is pervading in this universe,"}, {"start": 987.32, "end": 992.32, "text": " then the Lord gives special eyes to Arjuna to see."}, {"start": 992.32, "end": 994.32, "text": " Because sitting in one place,"}, {"start": 994.32, "end": 997.32, "text": " you cannot see the entire universe."}, {"start": 997.32, "end": 999.32, "text": " You know."}, {"start": 999.32, "end": 1003.32, "text": " We can only see to a certain extent."}, {"start": 1003.32, "end": 1007.32, "text": " And some of us will require the specs to see even,"}, {"start": 1007.32, "end": 1009.32, "text": " you know, what is there behind."}, {"start": 1009.32, "end": 1012.32, "text": " You know, that is our capacity."}, {"start": 1012.32, "end": 1015.32, "text": " So, the specific eyes were given to Arjuna"}, {"start": 1015.32, "end": 1017.32, "text": " so that Divya, Chakshu,"}, {"start": 1017.32, "end": 1023.32, "text": " so that he can see the entire universe sitting in one place."}, {"start": 1023.32, "end": 1025.3200000000002, "text": " And when he is seeing,"}, {"start": 1025.3200000000002, "end": 1031.3200000000002, "text": " he is also unable to find what is the Adhi, Madhyam and Anta."}, {"start": 1031.32, "end": 1033.32, "text": " He himself is admitting that."}, {"start": 1033.32, "end": 1037.32, "text": " nāntam na madhyam nāpunastavādhyam"}, {"start": 1037.32, "end": 1038.32, "text": " So, that's why,"}, {"start": 1038.32, "end": 1042.32, "text": " paśyāmi viśveśvara viśvarūpā"}, {"start": 1042.32, "end": 1045.32, "text": " So, Krishna's one universe"}, {"start": 1045.32, "end": 1046.32, "text": " and his universal form"}, {"start": 1046.32, "end": 1049.32, "text": " is so difficult to understand."}, {"start": 1049.32, "end": 1052.32, "text": " So, here that's what Maitreya is explaining."}, {"start": 1052.32, "end": 1055.32, "text": " yogamāyā bhalodayam"}, {"start": 1055.32, "end": 1057.32, "text": " The form,"}, {"start": 1057.32, "end": 1060.32, "text": " see, all the verses in the previous,"}, {"start": 1060.32, "end": 1062.32, "text": " you know, in the previous verses"}, {"start": 1062.32, "end": 1065.32, "text": " were describing the viśvarūpa."}, {"start": 1065.32, "end": 1069.32, "text": " Maitreya Rishi is explaining the viśvarūpa,"}, {"start": 1069.32, "end": 1072.32, "text": " how various things are getting manifest,"}, {"start": 1072.32, "end": 1077.32, "text": " various departments of the universal form."}, {"start": 1077.32, "end": 1079.32, "text": " And then here he is saying"}, {"start": 1079.32, "end": 1084.32, "text": " that universal form is manifested by yogamāyā."}, {"start": 1084.32, "end": 1088.32, "text": " One single manifestation of yogamāyā."}, {"start": 1088.32, "end": 1089.32, "text": " And then,"}, {"start": 1089.32, "end": 1094.32, "text": " there is not possible to estimate."}, {"start": 1094.32, "end": 1098.32, "text": " Upākartum means measure in totality."}, {"start": 1098.32, "end": 1102.32, "text": " Nobody can measure the Lord in totality."}, {"start": 1102.32, "end": 1104.32, "text": " Lord's own appellances"}, {"start": 1104.32, "end": 1107.32, "text": " and Lord's various potencies,"}, {"start": 1107.32, "end": 1110.32, "text": " nobody can appellate."}, {"start": 1110.32, "end": 1113.32, "text": " In fact, it is said that even Krishna doesn't,"}, {"start": 1113.32, "end": 1116.32, "text": " cannot estimate his own"}, {"start": 1116.32, "end": 1118.32, "text": " appellances and potencies."}, {"start": 1119.32, "end": 1123.32, "text": " Sometimes he himself gets surprised"}, {"start": 1123.32, "end": 1126.32, "text": " about his own appellances."}, {"start": 1126.32, "end": 1128.32, "text": " If that is the case,"}, {"start": 1128.32, "end": 1130.32, "text": " how can an ordinary human being"}, {"start": 1130.32, "end": 1133.32, "text": " can estimate the potencies of the Supreme Lord?"}, {"start": 1133.32, "end": 1136.32, "text": " Forget about entire potencies,"}, {"start": 1136.32, "end": 1137.32, "text": " even one universe,"}, {"start": 1137.32, "end": 1139.32, "text": " even that is also,"}, {"start": 1139.32, "end": 1140.32, "text": " in totality,"}, {"start": 1140.32, "end": 1142.32, "text": " to measure the one universe,"}, {"start": 1142.32, "end": 1144.32, "text": " that is also not possible."}, {"start": 1144.32, "end": 1146.32, "text": " So that's why Prabhupāda is saying,"}, {"start": 1146.32, "end": 1148.32, "text": " be cool-headed."}, {"start": 1149.32, "end": 1151.32, "text": " When you hear about Krishna,"}, {"start": 1151.32, "end": 1152.32, "text": " be cool-headed."}, {"start": 1152.32, "end": 1154.32, "text": " Don't try to measure,"}, {"start": 1154.32, "end": 1158.32, "text": " because you will not be successful."}, {"start": 1158.32, "end": 1162.32, "text": " And measure and come up with some speculative philosophies,"}, {"start": 1162.32, "end": 1166.32, "text": " that is a dangerous path."}, {"start": 1166.32, "end": 1168.32, "text": " So that's why,"}, {"start": 1168.32, "end": 1172.32, "text": " actually in Bhagavatam Krishna book it is explained,"}, {"start": 1172.32, "end": 1174.32, "text": " when the demigods,"}, {"start": 1174.32, "end": 1175.32, "text": " they know,"}, {"start": 1175.32, "end": 1177.32, "text": " they came to know about,"}, {"start": 1177.32, "end": 1181.32, "text": " that the Lord has appeared in the world."}, {"start": 1181.32, "end": 1184.32, "text": " When the Lord is in the womb of Devaki,"}, {"start": 1184.32, "end": 1185.32, "text": " the demigods,"}, {"start": 1185.32, "end": 1189.32, "text": " they appear in the prison."}, {"start": 1189.32, "end": 1190.32, "text": " They were,"}, {"start": 1190.32, "end": 1194.32, "text": " they were wanting to offer their prayers to Krishna."}, {"start": 1194.32, "end": 1195.32, "text": " And,"}, {"start": 1195.32, "end": 1198.32, "text": " they glorify the Lord,"}, {"start": 1198.32, "end": 1199.32, "text": " that,"}, {"start": 1199.32, "end": 1200.32, "text": " my Lord,"}, {"start": 1200.32, "end": 1203.32, "text": " now you are appearing in this world,"}, {"start": 1203.32, "end": 1206.32, "text": " in order to shatter all speculations"}, {"start": 1206.32, "end": 1210.32, "text": " about the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 1210.32, "end": 1213.32, "text": " Whatever speculations are there about the Supreme Lord,"}, {"start": 1213.32, "end": 1214.32, "text": " are put to rest,"}, {"start": 1214.32, "end": 1216.32, "text": " because,"}, {"start": 1216.32, "end": 1217.32, "text": " you know,"}, {"start": 1217.32, "end": 1218.32, "text": " by seeing you,"}, {"start": 1218.32, "end": 1220.32, "text": " by seeing your transcendental form,"}, {"start": 1220.32, "end": 1223.32, "text": " all these philosophies are put to rest."}, {"start": 1223.32, "end": 1224.32, "text": " Actually,"}, {"start": 1224.32, "end": 1226.32, "text": " that is one of the purposes of the Lord's,"}, {"start": 1226.32, "end": 1229.32, "text": " descent into this world."}, {"start": 1229.32, "end": 1231.32, "text": " He wants to show,"}, {"start": 1231.32, "end": 1233.32, "text": " who the Supreme Lord is."}, {"start": 1233.32, "end": 1235.32, "text": " And all the other speculations are,"}, {"start": 1235.32, "end": 1238.32, "text": " put to rest."}, {"start": 1238.32, "end": 1239.32, "text": " So that's why,"}, {"start": 1239.32, "end": 1241.32, "text": " Krishna's appearance is His mercy,"}, {"start": 1241.32, "end": 1242.32, "text": " because,"}, {"start": 1242.32, "end": 1243.32, "text": " the Vijnanam,"}, {"start": 1243.32, "end": 1244.32, "text": " the,"}, {"start": 1244.32, "end": 1246.32, "text": " the realized knowledge can,"}, {"start": 1246.32, "end": 1249.32, "text": " which is been explained by great sages,"}, {"start": 1249.32, "end": 1251.32, "text": " great Acharyas."}, {"start": 1251.32, "end": 1252.32, "text": " So Krishna,"}, {"start": 1252.32, "end": 1253.32, "text": " by His appearance,"}, {"start": 1253.32, "end": 1257.32, "text": " He proves that realized knowledge."}, {"start": 1257.32, "end": 1259.32, "text": " Like Brahma is the,"}, {"start": 1259.32, "end": 1262.32, "text": " original Acharya of our Parampara."}, {"start": 1262.32, "end": 1264.32, "text": " His realization is this,"}, {"start": 1264.32, "end": 1267.32, "text": " Adhyam Purana Purusham Navayavanamcha."}, {"start": 1267.32, "end": 1271.32, "text": " This is the realization of Brahmachrya."}, {"start": 1271.32, "end": 1273.32, "text": " And Krishna's appearance proves,"}, {"start": 1273.32, "end": 1275.32, "text": " the Vijnanam,"}, {"start": 1275.32, "end": 1279.32, "text": " the realized knowledge of all these Acharyas."}, {"start": 1279.32, "end": 1281.32, "text": " And then simultaneously,"}, {"start": 1281.32, "end": 1283.32, "text": " put to rest,"}, {"start": 1283.32, "end": 1286.32, "text": " all the philosophies of these frog philosophers."}, {"start": 1286.32, "end": 1287.32, "text": " Like in sixties,"}, {"start": 1287.32, "end": 1289.32, "text": " when Prabhupada went to America,"}, {"start": 1289.32, "end": 1290.32, "text": " there was a philosophy,"}, {"start": 1290.32, "end": 1291.32, "text": " that,"}, {"start": 1291.32, "end": 1293.32, "text": " God is dead now."}, {"start": 1293.32, "end": 1295.32, "text": " Why they are seeing that?"}, {"start": 1295.32, "end": 1298.32, "text": " Because there are so many problems in this world,"}, {"start": 1298.32, "end": 1299.32, "text": " that they are saying,"}, {"start": 1299.32, "end": 1300.32, "text": " God,"}, {"start": 1300.32, "end": 1302.32, "text": " God must have died by now."}, {"start": 1302.32, "end": 1303.32, "text": " Because after creation,"}, {"start": 1303.32, "end": 1304.32, "text": " all those things,"}, {"start": 1304.32, "end": 1305.32, "text": " you know,"}, {"start": 1305.32, "end": 1306.32, "text": " He must be very old,"}, {"start": 1306.32, "end": 1308.32, "text": " and probably died also."}, {"start": 1308.32, "end": 1310.32, "text": " This is their philosophy of,"}, {"start": 1310.32, "end": 1312.32, "text": " God."}, {"start": 1312.32, "end": 1314.32, "text": " So Prabhupada,"}, {"start": 1314.32, "end": 1315.32, "text": " in one place,"}, {"start": 1315.32, "end": 1316.32, "text": " he says,"}, {"start": 1316.32, "end": 1319.32, "text": " everybody used to think God is dead."}, {"start": 1319.32, "end": 1321.32, "text": " But now they understood,"}, {"start": 1321.32, "end": 1322.32, "text": " that the God is dead."}, {"start": 1322.32, "end": 1323.32, "text": " They understood,"}, {"start": 1323.32, "end": 1328.32, "text": " that the God is with Bhaktivedanta Swami."}, {"start": 1328.32, "end": 1330.32, "text": " So Prabhupada has,"}, {"start": 1330.32, "end": 1332.32, "text": " Prabhupada has proven,"}, {"start": 1332.32, "end": 1333.32, "text": " about God,"}, {"start": 1333.32, "end": 1334.32, "text": " about Krishna,"}, {"start": 1334.32, "end": 1335.32, "text": " he established,"}, {"start": 1335.32, "end": 1336.32, "text": " he,"}, {"start": 1336.32, "end": 1338.32, "text": " particularly,"}, {"start": 1338.32, "end": 1342.32, "text": " Prabhupada's famous conversations with his,"}, {"start": 1342.32, "end": 1345.32, "text": " disciples about the scientists."}, {"start": 1345.32, "end": 1346.32, "text": " Particularly,"}, {"start": 1346.32, "end": 1347.32, "text": " with Swaroop Dham,"}, {"start": 1347.32, "end": 1348.32, "text": " with Prabhu,"}, {"start": 1348.32, "end": 1350.32, "text": " and then many other,"}, {"start": 1350.32, "end": 1351.32, "text": " you know,"}, {"start": 1351.32, "end": 1352.32, "text": " disciples."}, {"start": 1352.32, "end": 1354.32, "text": " They used to ask a lot of questions,"}, {"start": 1354.32, "end": 1355.32, "text": " to Srila Prabhupada,"}, {"start": 1355.32, "end": 1357.32, "text": " about scientific,"}, {"start": 1357.32, "end": 1359.32, "text": " achievements of the,"}, {"start": 1359.32, "end": 1361.32, "text": " the scientists."}, {"start": 1361.32, "end": 1362.32, "text": " And then Prabhupada,"}, {"start": 1362.32, "end": 1363.32, "text": " very famously,"}, {"start": 1363.32, "end": 1365.32, "text": " used to use this word,"}, {"start": 1365.32, "end": 1367.32, "text": " frog philosophy."}, {"start": 1367.32, "end": 1369.32, "text": " And then he coined the word called,"}, {"start": 1369.32, "end": 1372.32, "text": " Dr. Frog."}, {"start": 1372.32, "end": 1373.32, "text": " You know,"}, {"start": 1373.32, "end": 1374.32, "text": " this is a,"}, {"start": 1374.32, "end": 1375.32, "text": " actually that's a Prabhupada's,"}, {"start": 1375.32, "end": 1376.32, "text": " beautiful,"}, {"start": 1376.32, "end": 1378.32, "text": " way of presentation,"}, {"start": 1378.32, "end": 1380.32, "text": " to summarize,"}, {"start": 1380.32, "end": 1381.32, "text": " you know,"}, {"start": 1381.32, "end": 1383.32, "text": " big, big concepts into one simple words."}, {"start": 1383.32, "end": 1386.32, "text": " Prabhupada used to coin these words,"}, {"start": 1386.32, "end": 1388.32, "text": " Dr. Frog."}, {"start": 1388.32, "end": 1390.32, "text": " Like in the conversation,"}, {"start": 1390.32, "end": 1391.32, "text": " you know,"}, {"start": 1391.32, "end": 1392.32, "text": " today in this book we are reading,"}, {"start": 1392.32, "end": 1393.32, "text": " Prabhupada summarizes,"}, {"start": 1393.32, "end": 1395.32, "text": " what is Vrindavan life?"}, {"start": 1395.32, "end": 1396.32, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 1396.32, "end": 1397.32, "text": " simple living,"}, {"start": 1397.32, "end": 1400.32, "text": " and high thinking."}, {"start": 1400.32, "end": 1402.32, "text": " So just one single word,"}, {"start": 1402.32, "end": 1404.32, "text": " Prabhupada has summarized,"}, {"start": 1404.32, "end": 1405.32, "text": " you know,"}, {"start": 1405.32, "end": 1408.32, "text": " the concept of what is Vrindavan life is."}, {"start": 1408.32, "end": 1409.32, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 1409.32, "end": 1412.32, "text": " this single liners of Prabhupada,"}, {"start": 1412.32, "end": 1414.32, "text": " very interesting to study."}, {"start": 1414.32, "end": 1415.32, "text": " You know,"}, {"start": 1415.32, "end": 1417.32, "text": " devotees can do little bit of research,"}, {"start": 1417.32, "end": 1418.32, "text": " and then you will see,"}, {"start": 1418.32, "end": 1420.32, "text": " lot of single liners like that."}, {"start": 1420.32, "end": 1422.32, "text": " Not even single liner,"}, {"start": 1422.32, "end": 1423.32, "text": " one word,"}, {"start": 1423.32, "end": 1424.32, "text": " Dr. Frog."}, {"start": 1424.32, "end": 1426.32, "text": " That summarizes,"}, {"start": 1426.32, "end": 1429.32, "text": " what Prabhupada wants to communicate about,"}, {"start": 1429.32, "end": 1432.32, "text": " the modern scientists."}, {"start": 1432.32, "end": 1434.32, "text": " One of the popular philosophy,"}, {"start": 1434.32, "end": 1436.32, "text": " those days was about,"}, {"start": 1436.32, "end": 1438.32, "text": " how the life comes from,"}, {"start": 1438.32, "end": 1440.32, "text": " chemicals."}, {"start": 1440.32, "end": 1441.32, "text": " Even now,"}, {"start": 1441.32, "end": 1443.32, "text": " many people believe,"}, {"start": 1443.32, "end": 1445.32, "text": " the life is actually coming from,"}, {"start": 1445.32, "end": 1447.32, "text": " chemical combination."}, {"start": 1447.32, "end": 1450.32, "text": " Somehow you mix up some chemicals,"}, {"start": 1450.32, "end": 1453.32, "text": " that will produce the life."}, {"start": 1453.32, "end": 1454.32, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 1454.32, "end": 1456.32, "text": " Prabhupada vehemently,"}, {"start": 1456.32, "end": 1459.32, "text": " he refuted this philosophy."}, {"start": 1459.32, "end": 1460.32, "text": " In fact,"}, {"start": 1460.32, "end": 1461.32, "text": " he fondly quotes,"}, {"start": 1461.32, "end": 1463.32, "text": " his disciple,"}, {"start": 1463.32, "end": 1465.32, "text": " Swaroop Dharmadhar Prabhu,"}, {"start": 1465.32, "end": 1467.32, "text": " who challenged the scientists."}, {"start": 1468.32, "end": 1470.32, "text": " One of the noble laureate,"}, {"start": 1470.32, "end": 1472.32, "text": " is presenting this philosophy,"}, {"start": 1472.32, "end": 1475.32, "text": " that the life has come from chemicals."}, {"start": 1475.32, "end": 1476.32, "text": " And then Swaroop Dharmadhar,"}, {"start": 1476.32, "end": 1477.32, "text": " he is there,"}, {"start": 1477.32, "end": 1478.32, "text": " in the crowd."}, {"start": 1478.32, "end": 1479.32, "text": " And then he says,"}, {"start": 1479.32, "end": 1480.32, "text": " okay,"}, {"start": 1480.32, "end": 1481.32, "text": " Mr. Scientist,"}, {"start": 1481.32, "end": 1483.32, "text": " I will give you all the chemicals,"}, {"start": 1483.32, "end": 1486.32, "text": " can you produce the life?"}, {"start": 1486.32, "end": 1487.32, "text": " And the scientist says,"}, {"start": 1487.32, "end": 1489.32, "text": " no, that I cannot do."}, {"start": 1489.32, "end": 1491.32, "text": " I can only stand and give classes,"}, {"start": 1491.32, "end": 1493.32, "text": " and lectures,"}, {"start": 1493.32, "end": 1494.32, "text": " and make some philosophies,"}, {"start": 1494.32, "end": 1496.32, "text": " and get some noble prizes."}, {"start": 1496.32, "end": 1497.32, "text": " But I can't do anything,"}, {"start": 1497.32, "end": 1499.32, "text": " and do anything in practical,"}, {"start": 1499.32, "end": 1500.32, "text": " you know,"}, {"start": 1500.32, "end": 1501.32, "text": " in practice."}, {"start": 1501.32, "end": 1502.32, "text": " You know,"}, {"start": 1502.32, "end": 1503.32, "text": " this is the,"}, {"start": 1503.32, "end": 1504.32, "text": " most of the people,"}, {"start": 1504.32, "end": 1505.32, "text": " these so-called scientists,"}, {"start": 1505.32, "end": 1507.32, "text": " they simply theorize."}, {"start": 1507.32, "end": 1508.32, "text": " If you talk,"}, {"start": 1508.32, "end": 1509.32, "text": " if you type,"}, {"start": 1509.32, "end": 1511.32, "text": " how the universe came,"}, {"start": 1511.32, "end": 1512.32, "text": " how the creation happened,"}, {"start": 1512.32, "end": 1515.32, "text": " so many philosophies."}, {"start": 1515.32, "end": 1516.32, "text": " Every month,"}, {"start": 1516.32, "end": 1517.32, "text": " I will see one,"}, {"start": 1517.32, "end": 1518.32, "text": " one philosophy,"}, {"start": 1518.32, "end": 1519.32, "text": " one,"}, {"start": 1519.32, "end": 1520.32, "text": " one theory."}, {"start": 1520.32, "end": 1521.32, "text": " But because,"}, {"start": 1521.32, "end": 1523.32, "text": " it has been proposed by Dr. Frog,"}, {"start": 1523.32, "end": 1525.32, "text": " people take it very seriously."}, {"start": 1525.32, "end": 1527.32, "text": " This is the unfortunate,"}, {"start": 1527.32, "end": 1529.32, "text": " unfortunate situation."}, {"start": 1529.32, "end": 1532.32, "text": " They don't go by the realized knowledge of a,"}, {"start": 1532.32, "end": 1535.32, "text": " of the Acharyas and the sages."}, {"start": 1535.32, "end": 1536.32, "text": " They have realized,"}, {"start": 1536.32, "end": 1538.32, "text": " because they have seen the absolute truth."}, {"start": 1538.32, "end": 1540.32, "text": " They have seen Krishna,"}, {"start": 1540.32, "end": 1541.32, "text": " and they are directly telling,"}, {"start": 1541.32, "end": 1543.32, "text": " he is now a Yavanamcha,"}, {"start": 1543.32, "end": 1545.32, "text": " he is a Parabrahma,"}, {"start": 1545.32, "end": 1548.32, "text": " but they don't want to accept that."}, {"start": 1548.32, "end": 1549.32, "text": " So this is,"}, {"start": 1549.32, "end": 1550.32, "text": " that's why Prabhupada is saying,"}, {"start": 1550.32, "end": 1552.32, "text": " he is concluding this pathport,"}, {"start": 1552.32, "end": 1554.32, "text": " saying that,"}, {"start": 1554.32, "end": 1556.32, "text": " be cool-headed,"}, {"start": 1556.32, "end": 1558.32, "text": " and be submissive."}, {"start": 1561.32, "end": 1562.32, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 1562.32, "end": 1564.32, "text": " remain very submissive,"}, {"start": 1564.32, "end": 1566.32, "text": " and then hear about the Lord."}, {"start": 1566.32, "end": 1568.32, "text": " From the Lord only,"}, {"start": 1568.32, "end": 1571.32, "text": " from the spiritual master."}, {"start": 1571.32, "end": 1572.32, "text": " From the Lord,"}, {"start": 1572.32, "end": 1574.32, "text": " or from the parampara of the Lord,"}, {"start": 1574.32, "end": 1576.32, "text": " if one hears about Krishna,"}, {"start": 1576.32, "end": 1577.32, "text": " then,"}, {"start": 1577.32, "end": 1580.32, "text": " that is the best way of understanding,"}, {"start": 1580.32, "end": 1582.32, "text": " the science of Krishna."}, {"start": 1582.32, "end": 1584.32, "text": " Any questions?"}, {"start": 1586.32, "end": 1588.32, "text": " So Prabhupada Kiya,"}, {"start": 1588.32, "end": 1590.32, "text": " Samad Bhagavatam Kiya."}]}